name: King County Open Data
description: The King County Open Data Project is an ongoing effort to release high-value, machine readable data sets to the public. The data sets currently available come from many areas of county government. Ongoing efforts to expand the data are in progress.

apis.name: King County Open Data
apis.description: King County is committed to making data open, accessible and transparent. This web site is designed to increase public access to high value, machine readable datasets from various departments in King County government. Additional data sets will be added over the coming months and we welcome feedback.
